channel.title: RuneScape 525 YETI!
channel.description: I found the model, and I took out all of the black triangles at every angle to save you some time. Also, I put it into .gzip format to save you time adding to your client. DON'T FORGET TO SAY INGAME [code]add model 45187[/code] NOT [code]::add model 45187[/code] NOT [code]/add model 45187[/code] [IMG]http://i490.photobucket.com/albums/rr265/cheese1111/Yeti.jpg[/img] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?ytkyoom2c4w]http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?ytkyoom2c4w[/url]
